                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 299r (at the bottom): ሕዳር፡ ፲፪ቀን፡ ፲፱፻፳፫ዓ.ም. ወይዘሮ፡ ግደይ፡ ተስፋ፡ ማርያም፡ ዓድዋ፡ አንድ፡ ምንጣፍ፡ ለቀርከበር፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ቤተክርስቲያን፡ የተለወ፡ ይኩና፡ መርህ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ዓሜን፡ ዓሜን።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The name of the donor(?), Mäzgäbä Śǝllase, is written interlineally in recent ink: e.g., fols. 3rb, 58vc, 110vbc, 150rb, 163rb, 184ra, 219rb, 243ra, 288rc, 299ra.&#xD;
- Short excerpts from commemorative notices for Taḫśaś, Ṭǝrr and Yäkkatit, in the main hand (?) on fol. 1v.&#xD;
- A few corrections are written over erasure or interlineally: fols. 25vab, 46rb, 69vb, 71ra, 256rb, 284ra, 288vc.&#xD;
- Erasures marked with parallel lines: fols. 16vc, 19ra, 26rb, 59rb, 65va, 71rab, 100va, 113vb, 152rc, 205ra, 240ra, 286ra, 290rb.&#xD;
- Crude drawings, scrivbbles in ink, pen and pencil: fols. 28v, 105v, 115v, 116r, 256v, 257v, 298v, 299v.</item>
